message.body: Are you free later today?
Sorry, it's super windy out. Im with some friends from home right now, probably won't be all day. Did you wanna do something?
I wanna get my side shaved at like 4pm today and I need someone to come with me!!! Gahhh
Dude. I will try to be back by then.
What time do you think you could be back??
I need to know so I can book it if you can
It's alright. Do you think you'd be able to come with me tomorrow or Thursday?
Sorry!!I don't think I can make it back by then.
Yeah tomorrow I'm free!
Ok I'll see if they have a slot free and all that
It's okay! It was super short notice.
Okay❤️✌️ sorry i couldn't figure out today!
Yo girl! We should do something today or tomorrow!
Yesssss!!! How about tomorrow? We can yolo it up somewhere- maybe see that show you were talking about?
Haha yeah sure. We can hang out tomorrow :) I'm not sure how much Gigi costs but I'll check it out.
Yo girl. Gigi is pretty expensive. It's at least $75....and the rush tix are still gonna be announced :/ wanna do something else?
Um yes, that would be wise I think:) I'll start looking.
Yo girl, you at home?
I am! Wassup?

Lolz, after I eat lunch, can I just come by and chill? Gotta do work but I'm alone in the suite so I was thinking maybe I could chill with you, figure out plans for tomorrow as well as do work at the same time
Haha awesome :) I'll come by after I finish eating!
Please do!!! That'd be awesome... I'm going crazy editing in here
Coolio :)
